cc:Work.dc:title: Misc - DrinkCarrier
cc:Work.dc:description:
A carrier for up to X number of drinks (Even Numbers Only) with a central handle. Features a double-layer base, rounded handle, and fully interlocking joints.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes DrinkCarrier Command line short: boxes DrinkCarrier
